    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but the \"agency\" you're talking about just feels like more work. why bother building a shelter when the storm is just going to win anyway? it feels more honest to just stop fighting it and accept the nothingness. wouldn't it be easier to just let go of the struggle and stop trying to pretend everything is okay?",
